gov.usgs.earthquake.nshmp.geo

Class LocationList.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.earthquake.nshmp.geo.LocationList.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    LocationList

    public static final class LocationList.Builder
extends Object
    A reusable builder of LocationLists. Repeat calls to build() will return multiple lists in series with each new list containing all the Locations of the one before it. Builders do not permit the addition of null elements.

    Use LocationList.builder() to create new builder instances.
